&lt;h1 id="the-ronco-principle"&gt;The Ronco Principle&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;January 2015&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No one, VC or angel, has invested in more of the top startups than Ron Conway. He knows what happened in every deal in the Valley, half the time because he arranged it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And yet he&amp;rsquo;s a super nice guy. In fact, nice is not the word. Ronco is good. I know of zero instances in which he has behaved badly. It&amp;rsquo;s hard even to imagine.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>A Venture SLA</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/a-venture-sla/</link><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2013 00:29:58 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/a-venture-sla/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/naval/zh/a-venture-sla.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
