&lt;h1 id="why-you-need-to-be-in-silicon-valley"&gt;Why You Need to be in Silicon Valley&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jan 17 2010&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For years I didn&amp;rsquo;t believe this. I thought that you could take advantage of the benefits of Boston, Seattle, NY, Austin – cheaper talent, no echo chamber, local Universities, etc.. But I give up. I found myself telling an entrepreneur why he had to be in Silicon Valley if he wanted to succeed. Most of my points are about Consumer Internet businesses&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Live Appearance</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/live-appearance/</link><pubDate>Fri, 15 Jan 2010 01:17:02 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/live-appearance/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/naval/zh/live-appearance.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
